{
  "stem": "2830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where we are going to go, we'd be better off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, who cares?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just thank for the day, another day to be alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, we were shipped [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] to Holland to another prison.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did I told you-- now you remind me about Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Felix.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kitty Hart.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was later in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right now, I'm telling you from prison to prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last prison was Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, you see a lot of prisoners-- or political, mostly political prisoners from all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were going-- they didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For me, I wind up-- we went-- they took us on a-- on trains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the kind of trains-- already different kind of trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We traveled a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was late, and full-- it was cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Finally--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the trains, everybody knows where they were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We traveled at day and at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you didn't eat--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You didn't-- couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was so surprising that you arrived-- arrived to Birkenau, and you hear music, orchestra playing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And we went out from the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were right away going in-- another selection, right or left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no-- it was just, I think, the older-- there were some older people or kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soldiers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went in a different-- different section.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went in a different section.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they take you to supposed to be shower or clean up, or get dressed, you know, in the uniforms that they give you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing before anything happens, they start to beat you.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
